Pseudocode for ex45 (wordFind)

Program will prompt the user to input the name of the output file for the changes.
It will then take the input from "ex45_input.txt" and read it
Then it will create a while loop that runs until the word utilize no longer exists
In this while loop it has 3 branches
    - Grab initial text where the word utilize is still in use.
    - Replace Utilize with Use.
    - Save to output when the word utilize is not included.
It will then create a new file with the name the user input before.